{"tid":642603,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"接左隻兩個月大貓返屋企","createTime":"2018-04-26T01:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T11:28:47.000Z","uid":30284,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"85befb65849a58e787cdc3dd04534f2a6953b831","tid":642603,"uid":30284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:50:45.000Z","msg":"幾日前夜晚接左隻兩個月大貓返屋企<br />\n<br />\n第一晚活力充沛到不得了<br />\n困籠cum埋布都不停叫不停伸手搲開捭布，叫足一晚<br />\n當然有時放佢出黎玩下探索下<br />\n<br />\n第二三日開始見佢冇晒精神 少左叫<br />\n成日坐或訓係籠入面 唔再好似第一晚咁咁有活力<br />\n<br />\n糧食方面就餵罐罐撈幼貓糧<br />\n佢就食哂罐罐同剩一半糧<br />\n一日一餐半倒<br />\n<br />\n好驚佢有咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n突然間由好動變到終日坐訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8840ed698bf620a1ab053d8bafd43287fe570839","tid":642603,"uid":150053,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:55:27.000Z","msg":"冇相想人點應？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b38a35afa79855004ed243931f10e4ea38b1171","tid":642603,"uid":49130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:00:23.000Z","msg":"有冇買玩具同佢玩?"},{"pid":"eb9c54d53077963704e1be28935e312aa8d3b35c","tid":642603,"uid":93395,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:00:43.000Z","msg":"叫完全日發現無人理咪唔出聲<br />\n<br />\n無圖都無人理你架啦"},{"pid":"32d2b15bbd220efa06bee605d009913c051e1cd4","tid":642603,"uid":30284,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"第一晚嘅時候<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/100424_2658d7a1255ba0fee1bef606e72c7c38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F100424_2658d7a1255ba0fee1bef606e72c7c38.png&h=63e2da30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/100426_63624377680d6e193dfa9a7a5e5f3044.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F100426_63624377680d6e193dfa9a7a5e5f3044.png&h=6b2dc610&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0babcf5beaaa5f04a758047edd2af6ee4dfadb2c","tid":642603,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:05:32.000Z","msg":"隻貓好靚呀."},{"pid":"ea98c494938133bf07b883dae99821f17804e882","tid":642603,"uid":22557,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁鬼老積既<br />\n睇第一張相唔覺得得2個月<br />\n格離執貓果隻都仲係成隻BB 咁"},{"pid":"fe5b4538e6e1eae39f0eaffedc496f05078c4a3e","tid":642603,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:07:44.000Z","msg":"俾著我喺個籠入面都會嘈嘈下冇心機嘈啦"},{"pid":"a3daf01b7ae61f87d4dbbbd0de850887ed3d9934","tid":642603,"uid":30284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:08:13.000Z","msg":"之後第二日開始就冇乜行動力同訓覺多<br />\n羽毛玩具果d都只係望但唔追拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebe2d1cc58f321adbf4b6c609685a7966357c50","tid":642603,"uid":125134,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:10:22.000Z","msg":"檢查下身體有冇癬,睇下耳仔乾唔乾淨, 有大量黑色耳屎有機會有耳蟎, 留意下眼屎分泌多唔多, 便便正唔正常同埋睇下食慾如何, 便便太爛唔成形有機會係D糧唔岩食,另外寄生蟲都會,以上咁多野都有機會拎到佢冇咩活力同埋食慾,同埋帶返黎之後起碼要7日後先幫佢杜蟲<br />\n<br />\n申利:自己經驗 有錯勿屌"},{"pid":"44b322c7c69a2d1c8a2ffe252aab1b9a551be166","tid":642603,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:10:59.000Z","msg":"唔洗困，俾佢岀黎探索啦"},{"pid":"f25c93122de508acbfd301fe30fe4fe57add13c6","tid":642603,"uid":125134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ebe2d1cc58f321adbf4b6c609685a7966357c50","tid":642603,"uid":125134,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:10